column10: In order to keep the floor of the event as dry as possible, we are asking all kegs be placed in keg tubs. Are you able to provide your own keg tubs for the event? column11: Please dump any excess liquids in a designated dumping area or outdoors.
column12: No flyers, stickers or anything that will create excess waste will be permitted at the event.
column13: Finally, please understand that this years Winter Warmer in using the space of another event (Lumaze) and we are asking everyone to please respect the property, instillations and work they have done to the site.
